d7fabfcc-b453-4f15-817c-36cb28d3c3a3.title: Belona
d7fabfcc-b453-4f15-817c-36cb28d3c3a3.text:
This guild contains minerals that haven't been found
anywhere else. I'm here to try and identify them.

1eec0bc9-81b1-4a10-ab6c-fd891db5f11f.title: Belona
1eec0bc9-81b1-4a10-ab6c-fd891db5f11f.text:
If you come across any unusual minerals when mining
here I'll take them off your hands. Don't worry, I'll
make it worth your while.

options.text: I dont want to receive minerals.
Can you combine my mining gloves?

cdc57ed2-95d6-4c26-b326-787a56bde41c.title: <player>
cdc57ed2-95d6-4c26-b326-787a56bde41c.text: What will you give me in return for these minerals?

f82472fb-7fa8-4c0b-b012-e93092fc9083.title: Belona
f82472fb-7fa8-4c0b-b012-e93092fc9083.text:
I have some gloves that will help you when Mining.
When you wear these gloves you'll find that some rocks
will instantly respawn.

326ff761-d69b-43d8-901f-9cddef9112c7.title: Belona
326ff761-d69b-43d8-901f-9cddef9112c7.text: So would you like to take a look?

37d20357-5640-45a3-9c2f-f26be34d2d32.title: Belona
37d20357-5640-45a3-9c2f-f26be34d2d32.text: Don't forget to come to me if you find any minerals.

370dce5d-e83c-414b-a638-748ee715ae3f.title: Belona
370dce5d-e83c-414b-a638-748ee715ae3f.text:
As you wish. You'll now find minerals when you mine
here. Let me know if you want to change this.

24a69e5c-6bec-42b0-80b6-eaf7993d5ad6.title: <player>
24a69e5c-6bec-42b0-80b6-eaf7993d5ad6.text: I dont want to receive minerals.

83a61bc7-516a-4b36-a3b1-69217468cc9e.title: Belona
83a61bc7-516a-4b36-a3b1-69217468cc9e.text:
Very well. You'll no longer find ant minerals when you
mine here. If you change you mind just let me know.

048254e0-b502-40ee-bdaf-96c19d476fd7.title: <player>
048254e0-b502-40ee-bdaf-96c19d476fd7.text: Can you combine my mining gloves?

1dccd876-8eb2-4aa4-81a5-dc1a8b1436b8.title: Belona
1dccd876-8eb2-4aa4-81a5-dc1a8b1436b8.text:
I guess I could combine some Mining gloves with some
Superior mining gloves. These new gloves would require
70 Mining to equip.

e5dacac1-d680-4695-8008-c04260affdae.title: Belona
e5dacac1-d680-4695-8008-c04260affdae.text:
It wouldn't be free though. I'd want 60 minerals in
return.

4e7e051f-a524-4059-9d65-a2069e536879.title: Belona
4e7e051f-a524-4059-9d65-a2069e536879.text:
You don't have the gloves for me to combine. You'll
need to bring me some Mining gloves and some
Superior mining gloves.

6c0f3a30-a697-4a60-aeac-57f1962f9047.title: Belona
6c0f3a30-a697-4a60-aeac-57f1962f9047.text: I required 60 minerals to combine your gloves!

becff4cc-43fe-4a76-8fee-814516716245.title: Belona
becff4cc-43fe-4a76-8fee-814516716245.text: Here are you newly combined Expert mining gloves.

3b240c00-8df6-4ae3-843e-29e79628a1fc.title: Belona
3b240c00-8df6-4ae3-843e-29e79628a1fc.text: Fair enough. I'll  be here if you change your mind.
